ATTRIBUTION REQUEST (Not legally required, but appreciated)
================================================================================

While the Apache-2.0 license does not require visible attribution in web
deployments, we kindly request that you:

  1. Keep "Powered by scView" in the application footer with a link to
     the project repository (this is the default configuration)

  2. Consider contributing improvements back to the project to help
     the open source community

  3. Let us know about your deployment - we'd love to hear how scView
     is being used!

Thank you for supporting open source software!

